# Styling

## CSS framework

Bootstrap 3 (`^3.3.7`), imported as LESS source via `@import "~bootstrap/less/bootstrap.less"` in `petclinic.less`.

## LESS files

All styles under `client/src/styles/less/`:

- `petclinic.less` — Main entry; imports Bootstrap, custom overrides, typography, header, responsive
- `typography.less` — `@font-face` for Varela Round (body) and Montserrat (headings)
- `header.less` — Navbar and branding styles
- `responsive.less` — Media query adjustments

## Conventions

- Use Bootstrap 3 grid classes (`col-sm-*`, `col-md-*`) for layout
- Use Bootstrap 3 component classes (`btn btn-default`, `table table-striped`, `form-horizontal`, `form-group`, `form-control`)
- Icons: Glyphicons (`glyphicon glyphicon-*`)
- Custom classes (`.xd-container`, `.error-page`, `.table-filter`) supplement Bootstrap
- Override Bootstrap variables in LESS to change theme colors — do not use inline styles for theming
- Fonts: Varela Round (body), Montserrat (headings), loaded from `client/src/styles/fonts/`
